name: Tiny Device #04: hen.link
description: This #OBJKT is an appreciation collab with https://twitter.com/playnft, he is giving away free short links to everyone who wants them. It visualizes how your long $tezos address turns into a convenient and short link if you got it from @playnft (dm on twitter). Half of the minted #OBJKT's were sent to @playnft. The data is not updated in real time, but pretty often. Made by https://twitter.com/neelts.
